{"tid":442985,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"黑氣！赫特遭電單車幫打劫","createTime":"2017-10-21T08:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T08:45:05.000Z","uid":91116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f035c976477ac7003c02edea86b5f5c6f4f3216","tid":442985,"uid":91116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T08:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/2/272/19320439272/19324521263_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F2%2F272%2F19320439272%2F19324521263_600x399.jpg&h=0499a575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Nw2Q7gf%2BvCm05u0rtT3%2F2gHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=bfcbd75c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】赫特於周五英超3度從網窩拾皮球，原來這位英格蘭門將早已黑氣纏身，近日在韋斯咸訓練場附近被電單車幫打劫，手錶、智能電話和銀包都被搶去。<br />\n<br />\n30歲的韋斯咸門將赫特（Joe Hart）成為電單車幫最新受害者，據了解，赫特完成英格蘭對立陶宛的世盃外任務後，回到韋斯咸的查特韋爾希斯訓練場操練，豈料不幸地遇到電單車幫打劫，據悉事件發生在一個加油站附近。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士向英國《太陽報》透露，「兩輛電單車上有3名劫匪，當赫特回到車上拿起電話時，劫匪就包圍著他。我想他們還搶了他的手錶和錢包。」另一名消息人士說，「赫特沒有受傷，但他很震驚。他是一個強健的大人物，要很大膽才能打劫到他。如果這些事都能發生在英格蘭守門員身上，那麼這種情況都可能發生在任何人身上。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"d108c7730009f6fdbf444bfbc1aa5bab35d4caca","tid":442985,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T08:39:46.000Z","msg":"幾把刀都驚<br />\n點去俄羅斯守龍牙"},{"pid":"07580a18de5934b74ff351582e143e9e9f1118b9","tid":442985,"uid":73748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T08:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾把刀都驚<br />\n點去俄羅斯守龍牙</blockquote><br />\n去坐姐"},{"pid":"ef97cc938ffb1bdabf3e51e58476795dba98cb09","tid":442985,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T08:41:35.000Z","msg":"咁撚高都有人打劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"